Wednesday, May 29, 1996

MERIT DOCKET

94-2176. State ex rel. Heller v. Indus. Comm.

Franklin County, No. 93AP-967. On motion to dismiss by Industrial Commission. Motion to dismiss sustained. Cause dismissed.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer, Cook and Stratton, JJ., concur.
